songs.title: Soja Djiki DESETKOM I DAMOM _dr_Khans
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Nama chopper je u studiju,
([adlib] - „chop-chop“)
pa malo jači flex
([delay] - „flex… flex…“)
Njene gole noge uviju,
([BV low] - „mmm…“)
pa malo jači sex
([reverb] - „jači sex…“)
Voli crnu metalurgiju
([FX grime] - „clang-clang“)
kad pati kalim bes
([growl] - „grrr…“)
U Audiju burgiju balavila ko pez
([engine rev] - vrrrroom)
Bezvez kez, dental sticks,
([chopped] - „kez-kez“)
bezveze, tims and tricks
([adlib] - „tricks… tricks…“)
Ko Vaskez, muscle build,
([BV gang] - „muscle, muscle“)
njima ide spomenik,
([echo] - „spomenik…“)
Pa polis (fucking flece)
([siren distant] - wiiiu-wiiiu)
Flight to Swiss, money moves
([cash FX] - „shhhh“)
Give me please, dobar niz, u biznisu Dibidus
([tapestop] - „di-bi-dus…“)

[Chorus]
Rani sati jutarnji,
([pad rise] - whoooom)
dižemo se skupa,
([gang BV] - „skupa, skupa“)
Ekipa prava, srcem jaka grupa
([chant] - „u-u-uuu“)
kad je dobro i kad nije
([echo] - „kad nije…“)
Držimo se zajedno,
([BV] - „zajedno…“)
uzori ulice, nadahnuti pravdom
([street FX] - distant traffic)
Sunce se rađa, ceo grad još spava
([soft BV] - „spava…“)
Mi na nogama, uveliko bistra glava
([head nod FX] - tkk)
Da bi biznis bio strava, mora da se radi
([chant] - „radi, radi…“)
Nema zastoja, zlato se iz blata vadi
([FX shovel] - shkrr)
Ko ti je u životu nek razume ko i shvati
([spoken BV] - „razumi, shvati…“)
Da bi danas znao ovo prvo mora da se pati
([delay] - „mora da se pati…“)
Onda presek stanja, činjenica se prihvati
([BV] - „prihvati…“)
Pa kud koji mili moj ' koliko ko sebi zahvati
([crowd murmur] - „ey, ey…“)

[Verse 2]
To je petak, kriva slika,
([FX camera] - click)
vama smešna svaka spika,
([chopped] - „spika-spika“)
Moj je Šoja, bratska dika,
([gang chant] - „Šo-ja!“)
metak primam za tog lika
([gun cock FX, low] - chk)
Ide hajp, u gađanju prvi
([adlib] - „hajp, hajp…“)
to je taktika
([echo] - „taktika…“)

[Instrumental Chops]
([scratch] - krk-krk)
([glitch vox] - „hey! hey!“)
([bass stab] - boom)

[Verse 3]
Moje srce lupa, lupa, ono tera 200 pumpa
([heartbeat FX] - thump-thump-thump)
Dobra nestane, koliko grama na metama smo mupa
([sirena daleko] - wiiiu)
Ova upala mi usta, njena usta cela buksna
([adlib] - „buksna…“)
A telo ti kao fuksa i belo  iz Beneluksa
([FX] - „beneluks… lux…“)

Putem do uspeha svi kažu nije lako
([spoken BV] - „nije lako…“)
Prave se pametni, al niko ne zna kako
([crowd] - „kako, kako…“)
Ovako il onako znam da boriću se jako
([chant] - „jako! jako!“)
Ustajanje rano, vožnja samo desnom stranom
([engine low] - vrrr)
Ubijanje sebe, tako dan za danom
([clock FX] - tik-tak)
Kao na zadatku tajnom dok ne pronađeš taj šablon
([whisper] - „tajno… šablon…“)
Odavno shvatio da nije sve sjajno i bajno
([BV] - „nije bajno…“)
Borim se za mesto koje će mi biti trajno
([echo] - „trajno… trajno…“)

[Chorus]
I nude mi dobar talon, započinjem tablom
([card FX] - shuffle)
Vi tri na karte - duplo, karo desetkom i damom
([chip FX] - clack)
Ko sotona pred Bogom šetam se tamo i vamo
([adlib] - „tamo-vamo…“)
Ne polarizujem sijam, obavijam ih sve tamom
([FX dark pad] - whooom)

[Verse 4]
Šole čakija golema, pada belo sad za pola
([knife FX] - shing)
Čuda mafija problema kada gejam punim borac
([phone buzz] - bzzz)
Krijem se, izmičem,
([echo] - „izmičem… izmičem…“)
dok pokušavam da shvatim igru
([BV low] - „igru…“)
Sklanjam se od svakog zla da bi spavao na miru
([sigh] - haaah)
Jedno bez drugog ne ide,
kao dirke na klaviru,
([piano FX] - pling-pling)
kao lav (borim se)
([growl] - rrrr)
da se ne udavim u viru.
([water FX] - shhhhlosh)

songs.title: Takking the next plane_Hardcore_Pop_1
songs.lyrics:
[Verse]
It's been a while since I called you
([dial tone] - tuu-tu-tuu)
I'm dialing in now
([keypad beeps] - bip-bip-bip)
Been a while since you heard my voice
([phone line hiss] - shhhh)
But you can hear me now
([soft reverb] - „hear me now…“)
It's been a while since I touched down
([landing gear thump] - thud)
But I'm touching down now
([airport ambience] - mmmrum)

[Chorus]
I just want to see you
([echo] - „see you, see you…“)
I just want to see you
([BG vox] - ooo-ooo)
I just want to see you
([delay] - „see you, see you…“)
I just want to see you
([soft sigh] - haaah)

[Verse 2]
It's been a while since I called you
([ringback tone] - triiim-triiim)
I'm dialing in now
([key click] - tik-tik-tik)
Been a while since you heard my voice
([mic breath] - ffff)
But you can hear me now
([stereo whisper] - „can you hear me?“)
It's been a while since I touched down
([wheel rumble] - rrrrmm)
But I'm touching down now
([PA chime] - ding-dong)

[Chorus]
I just want to see you
([BG harmonies] - ahh-ahh)
I just want to see you
([echo] - „see you…“)
I just want to see you
([clap reverb] - clap…clap)
I just want to see you
([sub swell] - whooom)

[Bridge]
I just want to see you
([chopped vox] - „see- see- see you“)
I just want to see you
([delay ping-pong] - „you… you…“)
I just want to see you
([BG oooh] - ooo-oo)
I just want to see you
([heartbeat] - thump-thump)
I just want to see you
([riser] - wooooosh)
I just want to see you
([stereo whisper] - „just you…“)
I just want to see you
([filtered vox] - „see you“)
I just want to see you
([pad swell] - aaaaah)

[Verse]
I still remember the first time
([vinyl soft] - pft)
Our timezones aligned
([clock tick] - tik-tak)
And your voice came through the line
([phone crackle] - krrrsh)
And I know that I always say
([BG hum] - mmm)
That I wish you weren't so far away
([distant echo] - „far away…“)
But we both know I could solve that in a day
([whoosh] - shhaaa)

[Pre-Chorus]
And what good is talking
([filter sweep] - ffff)
When I could just
([snare build] - tchk-tchk-tchk)
Take the next flight?
([jet roar] - vrrrROOOM)

[Chorus]
I'm getting on that plane tonight
([gang BG] - „tonight, tonight…“)

[Verse 2]
One day soon you'll be so close
([close whisper] - „so close…“)
And the only thing separating us will be clothes
([cheeky BG] - heh)
Maybe I'm crazy but I know
([reverb] - „I know…“)
That I don't know much
([sub drop] - boom)
But what I know
([snap] - snap)
Is I met you once and now I can't let you go
([BG adlib] - „can’t let you go…“)
And we both know how this story goes
([reverse swell] - whoooosh)

[Chorus]
I'm getting on that plane tonight
([BG chant] - „plane tonight…“)
I'm getting on that plane tonight
([echo] - „tonight, night, night…“)

songs.plays: Bajkkeri_2_Hardcore_Pop_2v5A dark Serbian dancehall riddim with a cold,urban feel,The tempo is mid–fast,the groove built around a heavy,syncopated dembow pattern with hard-hitting kick,sharp snare and crisp offbeat hats,The clean guitar becomes a more aggressive,slightly overdriven pluck riff,playing short,catchy minor-key phrases with a metallic,neon shimmer,doubled by a thin synth lead for that club feel,The bass turns into a thick,sub-heavy 808 / synth bass,following a mean root–fifth–octave pattern with occasional slides,pushing the rhythm forward and giving it that “street” pressure,Drums are tight and punchy,side-chained to the bass for bounce,with extra percussion (rims,claps,small fills) to emphasize the offbeats,No vocals – only occasional chopped crowd shouts and siren FX,drenched in short delays and gated reverbs,Overall mix is modern and loud,with focused low-end,bright transients,and subtle reverb on melodic elements,creating a dark neon alley vibe – half Berlin street,‑arabic,‑violin,‑static,‑low-energy,‑mellow

songs.title: Kko te tera_Hardcore_Pop_2
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Jesi ti,Pope, kadio matru???.....
([Laughter in background] - hahaha)
([Lighter flick] - chk)
([female adlib] - mmm-aaa)

Ne prilazi, bejbi, ne znaš ko sam ja
([breathy BV] - mmm-aaah)
Maska na licu, a vidim, goriš sva
([vocal chop] - ya-ya)
Noć je hladna, oči crvene k'o lava
([sub-bass rumble] - rrrrr)
U klubu senke, al' u meni cela drama
([crowd murmur] - mmmrum)


---

[Refren]
Ne prilazi (ne), nisam tvoj spas
([female echo] - „nisam tvoj spas…”)
Ja sam onaj od kog’ ti drhti glas
([BV airy] - aaah-aaah)
Noćas sam dim, sutra nestaću skroz
([delay] - „nestaaaću…”)
Ti me tražiš, al’ proš’o je voz
([FX] - tschuuu / train-whoosh)


---

[Verse 1]
Rolex na ruci, al’ vreme nije važno
([watch tick] - tik-tak)
Nisam tu, a osećaš se prazno
([low BV hum] - mmm)
Kol’ko još puta reći ćeš mi „ne“
([chopped BV] - „ne-ne-ne“)
Kad ćeš da se predaš i priznaš mi sve
([breathy BV] - haaah)

Ponoćni poziv, znamo šta to znači
([phone ring] - brr-brr)
U glasu ti trema, al’ telo kaže „go“
([BV whisper] - „go, go…“)
Na stolu je piće, al’ u glavi lom
([glass clink] - clink)
Sa tobom sam vatra, bez tebe siv je dom
([fire FX] - fssshh)

Ko te to tera da bežiš od mene,
([female adlib] - „bežiš… bežiš…“)
U snovima tvojim vodim se pod „ne smem“
([reverb] - „ne smem…“)
Ti bežiš od mene, a u sebi me kriješ
([BV close] - mmm-aaah)
U ogledalu tuđa lica — iza njih se kriješ
([echo tail] - „kriješ… kriješ…“)
